{
  "stem": "22856.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were represented-- representative of Poland, of Jewish and Polish [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] trade and commerce.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yes, they were.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But they were limited, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, probably Gestapo.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was the Jewish [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] organization, a Jewish-- how to call this?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Representation, who contacted the German and they received the-- because in the beginning, it was not regulated.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But later on, everybody got some rations, and we had to produce the ration if you wanted to buy in the shop.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I couldn't give you now immediately the names, but it was, generally speaking, the-- the head of the SS or German police-- Polizei, Polizei.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the beginning it was very, very difficult.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You were-- you couldn't find a place where only one family lived.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were in a special position to got-- to get a room in our friend's place, so we could say that we were together with them.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But there were cases where two, three, or four, sometimes, families had to divide their room with partition, and where children were, it wasn't a easy living condition at all.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What was-- proper--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In the beginning, they allowed you, but then it was restricted because of transport and so on.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think ghetto was about 30,000 or 40,000 people, but later on it was dwindled.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When we went to the Plaszow camp, it was only 20,000 because the other part was all of it reduced for sending out to-- to concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were always deportations, because there were always reason to find people on the streets or at homes.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes, there were.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Probably it was the Jewish police-- poli-- policy to leave this alone to Polish-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I don't know how to call it.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
